give @s written_book[written_book_content={title:"Juggernaut Instructions",author:"BubkisLord",generation:1,pages:[\
{"text":"Juggernaut\n\nOne or more Juggernauts hunt a team of Runners. Runners must replenish stations before they are wiped out. Juggernaut wins by eliminating all Runners. Runners win by completing enough stations."},\
{"text":"Setup\n\nPlayers pick a Juggernaut(s) randomly. Survivors pick a Runner kit. You get 25s to prep and find a station before the Juggernaut spawns at one of the 3 farthest spawn points."},\
{"text":"Lives\n\nEach Runner starts with (Juggernaut count + 1) lives, min 2. Survivor kit gets +1 life. Lose all lives = eliminated to spectator. Juggernaut has 1 life - kill it and Runners win instantly."},\
{"text":"Winning\n\nReplenish stations to win! Stand within 3 blocks of a station, Juggernaut must be 12+ blocks away, no Banishment Glyph nearby. Complete enough stations before lives run out."},\
{"text":"Station Strategy\n\nPrioritise risky/exposed stations early (e.g. the bridge). Save the stations far apart for last - it makes the Juggernaut work harder to patrol them."},\
{"text":"Station Particles\n\nEnd Rod = being replenished\nTotem = station present\nPurple Witch = Juggernaut nearby, warning!\nFlame / White Smoke = blocked by Glyph"},\
{"text":"The Chase\n\nGet too close to the Juggernaut and you enter Chase. While chased you passively replenish the top station, but the Juggernaut hunts harder. Outrun them to escape Chase."},\
{"text":"Healing\n\nStand still while a hurt ally crouches near you to heal them. Sneak alone to slowly self-heal. More health lost takes longer to heal - stay safe to heal faster."},\
{"text":"Runner Kits\n\nGuide - pure replenisher\nEscapist - mobility/evasion\nRogue - stealth/info\nMedic - healing\nScout - spots Juggernaut\nSurvivor - extra life, tanky"},\
{"text":"More Runner Kits\n\nGhost - max stealth, high risk\nEngineer - portable stations\nTrickster - disorients the Juggernaut in chase"},\
{"text":"Juggernaut Kits\n\nClassic - one-shot crit axe\nDragon - ranged breath, flight\nHunter - mark & pursue, bow\nWarlock - area lockdown glyphs\nPredator - permanent stealth"},\
{"text":"More Juggernaut Kits\n\nSpirit Walker - short CD teleport\nWitch Doctor - stacking buffs\nTimekeeper - damage tracks\nChameleon - disguises as Runners\nFishmonger - trident mobility\nKnight - horse & jousting spear"},\
{"text":"Tips to Win\n\nRunners: rotate stations, do not group up, break line of sight with terrain.\nJuggernaut: control chokepoints, track recently-replenished stations, deny healing windows."},\
{"text":"Reset\n\nIf anything breaks, run /function minecraft:reset to fix the game state."}\
]}]
